## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability and scope of the sources consulted. The complexity of violent crime means that not all factors can be fully explored in a single report. Additionally, cultural and regional differences in crime causation are not extensively covered, which may affect the generalizability of the findings. Further research is needed to explore these aspects in more detail.

